Let Beer52's beer tasters take you on a journey of taste discovery around the world. With a new country of theme to discover each month, you'll enjoy a variety of styles.  Each box contains 8 different beers each month, along with a 100-page magazine and a tasty snack. From hoppy IPAs and German classics, to smooth stouts and interesting Belgian brews, there's a world of beer to discover.  Don't like dark beers? No problem, you can set your own taste preferences when setting up your deliveries.